@node usage "usage"
                                 @{b}Usage@{ub}
           (1) - > WordList: 
                   ---------
               - > Actual Progress of WordList RecoVer is an Soft RecoVer
               - > Basicly list All The Password You USE Most time 
               - > see included WrdBox/Pwlist & List Your Passwords Down
               - > & Save it As what ever Filename You Like long as You can
               - > Remmember.

           (2) - > FileName .Zip
                   -------------
               - > Copy Your .Zip Archive to ZipBox/
               

           (3) - > RecoVer From
                   ------------
               - > You Are RecoVering From .Zip what ever Your .Zip Archive
               - > So Open Your .Zip Archive With Voodo-X or other Programs 
               - > & Note Down FileName You Want To RecoVer then Type in That
               - > at RecoVer From.    

           (4) - > example Usage
                   -------------
                 1. Run Zip-RecoVer Click in Wordlist then type Pwlist then Enter
                 2. Click in FileName .Zip & Type Sample.Zip then Enter.
                 3. Click in RecoVer From & Type 123.txt then Enter.

                 4. After You Have Done 1/2/3 Then Click Start Button .. Thats All
                              ==============


@endnode

